markdown <<MARKDOWN
## Alice's Game Controller

#### Alice designed a game controller for users with mobility issues. It allows users to lightly tap specific locations on the device instead of having to press a button down.

#### In user testing, Alice noticed that users with mobility issues had better experiences than those who were used to pressing buttons. In fact, the users without mobility issues encountered a bug when pressing down too hard on the sensors.

#### Now Alice needs to make a decision about what to do with this new information

